<div class="jumbotron">
  <img src="/images/jumbotron.jpg" alt="{{brand}}" />
  <div class="container jumbo-content">
    <h1>Mobile productivity made easy.</h1>
    <form class="jumbotron-form" action="/results" method="GET">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-offset-3 col-lg-6">
          <input type="text" class="form-control" id="location" name="location" placeholder="Enter your zip code" autofocus>
          <button type="submit" class="btn btn-default">Search</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </form>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="container-fluid">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-4">
      <div class="thumbnail">
        <img class="feature-image" src="/images/feature_1.jpg" alt="Find Your Workplace">
        <div class="caption">
          <h3>Find Your Workplace</h3>
          <p>Powered by the Workfrom API, Office Anywhere offers thousands of locations to help pinpoint your next meeting, group project, or study session.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-4">
      <div class="thumbnail">
        <img class="feature-image" src="/images/feature_2.jpg" alt="Know Before You Go">
        <div class="caption">
          <h3>Know Before You Go</h3>
          <p>How's the WiFi?  Can I take my dog?  Use Office Anywhere to ensure your next work destination has all the ammenities your team requires.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-4">
      <div class="thumbnail">
        <img class="feature-image" src="/images/feature_3.jpg" alt="Share Your Experiences">
        <div class="caption">
          <h3>Share Your Experiences</h3>
          <p>Each location has a comments section for Office Anywhere users to share their experiences.  Create an account and start adding your feedback!</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
